{"tid":1194360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場新聞：民陣籲市民終點留步　預演包圍立法會","createTime":"2019-06-09T08:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T09:13:47.000Z","uid":47714,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"02a1bbf09c147f1590df4e72718e99cf1bd4278c","tid":1194360,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T08:54:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/6-9-大遊行-民陣籲市民終點留步-預演包圍立法會/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F6-9-%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E7%B1%B2%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E7%B5%82%E9%BB%9E%E7%95%99%E6%AD%A5-%E9%A0%90%E6%BC%94%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%2F&d=QsQvn9KnS4zrnMXWGBKJeNDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=8848a601\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F6-9-%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E6%B0%91%E9%99%A3%E7%B1%B2%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E7%B5%82%E9%BB%9E%E7%95%99%E6%AD%A5-%E9%A0%90%E6%BC%94%E5%8C%85%E5%9C%8D%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%2F&h=5dd82fa1\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/6-9-大遊行-民陣籲市民終點留步-預演包圍立法會/</a><br />\n<br />\n民陣今日發起反送中大遊行。民陣下午4時宣布，將會預演包圍立法會，呼籲市民遊行到終點立法會外時留步，希望可以「逼爆立法會道，令警察開放添美道」。<br />\n<br />\n民陣在FB發出呼籲，請市民到達目的地時先留步，「我們要靠人數逼爆立法會道，令警察開放添美道！」民陣指，市民之後可以沿著添馬公園離開，到時大會將有航拍機拍攝添美道及添馬公園，「我們要告訴中共，香港政府，國際知道，香港人係有能力包圍立法會的！」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/posts/2293093760738002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FCivilHumanRightsFront%2Fposts%2F2293093760738002&d=QsQvn9KnS4zrnMXWGBKJeNDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=dbfba688\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/CivilHumanRightsFront/posts/2293093760738002</a>"},{"pid":"693ef9627f3daab78971d8eca131fcb77eef9d0d","tid":1194360,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T09:05:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51fabfdfe828785b9472a045311d76ece4adb664","tid":1194360,"uid":19552,"li